SUMMARY:Hamilton Saturday Salsa
DESCRIPTION:Language Exchange Toronto - Se Habla English & Spanish\n🔥 *
 *SalsaSoul Saturdays is heating up the winter season in Hamilton!**\n\nEve
 ry third Saturday of the month\, the Main Stage at 747 King Street E trans
 forms into a vibrant hub of salsa and bachata\, welcoming dancers of all l
 evels for unforgettable nights of rhythm\, community\, and pure fun.\n\nGu
 ests are invited to arrive as doors open at **7:30 p.m.**\, followed by a 
 **Beginner Salsa Lesson at 8:00 p.m.**\, perfect for newcomers or anyone l
 ooking to warm up. The energy rises as the **Latin Dance Party kicks off f
 rom 9:00 p.m. to 1:00 a.m.**\, featuring a lively mix of primarily salsa a
 nd bachata.\n\nAdmission is **$20 for the party** or **$25 including the l
 esson**\, and each ticket includes a complimentary drink. Advance tickets 
 are also available through the event’s ticket link:\nhttps://www.zeffy.c
 om/en-CA/ticketing/salsa-soul-saturday-jan-17--2026\n\nThe venue offers **
 free on-site and neighbourhood parking**\, along with a **cash bar** for g
 uests to enjoy throughout the night. No partner or prior dance experience 
 is required—everyone is welcome to join the celebration.\n\nSalsaSoul Sa
 turdays promises fiery music\, warm community vibes\, and a dance floor re
 ady for all who want to move.\n\n**Winter just got a lot hotter.**\n\nMore
  Information:\nhttps://www.salsasoulproductions.com/\nhttps://www.facebook
 .com/salsasoulproductions/\n\nSee you there....\nHéctor
