BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Toronto Social Events
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/toronto/
UID:event_313604232@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260322T025647Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260322T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260322T130000
SUMMARY:English Spanish Language Conversation
DESCRIPTION:Language Exchange Toronto - Se Habla English & Spanish\n**Span
 ish Language Conversation Toronto** is part of ***Se Habla***\, a worldwid
 e community made up of 9 Meetup groups from 9 different cities across 6 co
 untries. Join us and don't miss the opportunity to speak with native speak
 ers.\n\n**Five years of meeting online.** Don’t wait—become part of ou
 r supportive international network of like-minded people and make friends 
 all over the world.\n\n**We meet on the following days:**\n\n* Monday\n* W
 ednesday\n* Friday\n* Saturday\n* Sunday\n\nWith a one-time donation\, you
  can join the meetings as many times as you like and stay as long as you w
 ish.\n\n**Format**\nDepending on attendance and nationality\, small groups
  are formed with 4-6 people:\n\n* 2 native English speakers\n* 2 native Sp
 anish speakers\n* 1 native speaker of another language\n\nThe meetings las
 t for 2 hours and are divided into 4 periods:\n\n* 30 minutes speaking in 
 English\n* 30 minutes speaking in Spanish\n* 30 minutes speaking in Englis
 h\n* 30 minutes speaking in Spanish\n\nPlease note that **we speak half of
  the time in English and half in Spanish.** We help each other learn both 
 languages.\n\n**After two hours**\, everyone returns to the main room to m
 eet all participants and take a group screenshot. If you have time\, you
 ’re welcome to stay and continue the conversation for as long as you lik
 e.\n\n**Community**\n**We have 9 MeetUp groups meeting at the same time** 
 (Mexico City\, Calgary\, Vancouver\, Toronto\, New York\, London\, Los Ang
 eles\, Medellin\, and Santiago de Chile). However\, during the exchange\, 
 you will meet people not only from these cities but also from all over the
  world.\n\nYou can get the link to our 9 MeetUp groups by visiting any of 
 the following pages:\n[https://se-habla.com/spanish-meetup/](https://se-ha
 bla.com/spanish-meetup/)\n[https://se-habla.com/english-meetup/](https://s
 e-habla.com/english-meetup/)\n\n**One-Time Donation**\nFor over four years
 \, the meetings were free\, but starting last October\, I am requesting a 
 **ONE-TIME DONATION** to access the meetings and help to cover the costs o
 f the 9 MeetUp Groups.\n\nYou can make the one-time donation at the link b
 elow. Afterward\, PayPal will redirect you to a page where you'll find the
  Zoom link to join the meeting.\n[https://se-habla.com/language-exchange/]
 (https://se-habla.com/language-exchange/)\n\nIf you have already made a do
 nation and don't have the Zoom link\, please contact me.\n\n**Please don
 ’t hesitate to reach out if you have any further questions.**\n\nSee you
  soon\,\n**Héctor Fuentes**
