SUMMARY:Conversation in Spanish & English Practice Online
DESCRIPTION:Language Exchange Toronto - Se Habla English & Spanish\n**Engl
 ish and Spanish Language Exchange Toronto** is part of ***Se Habla***\, a 
 worldwide community made up of 9 Meetup groups from 9 different cities acr
 oss 6 countries. Join us and don't miss the opportunity to speak with nati
 ve speakers.\n\n**Five years of meeting online.** Don’t wait—become pa
 rt of our supportive international network of like-minded people and make 
 friends all over the world.\n\n**We meet on the following days:**\n\n* Mon
 day\n* Wednesday\n* Friday\n* Saturday\n* Sunday\n\nWith a one-time donati
 on\, you can join the meetings as many times as you like and stay as long 
 as you wish..\n\n**Format**\n**Conversation Rooms (All levels)**\nDependin
 g on attendance and nationality\, small groups are formed with 4-6 people:
 \n\n* 2 native English speakers\n* 2 native Spanish speakers\n* 1 native s
 peaker of another language\n\nThe meetings last for 2 hours and are divide
 d into 4 periods:\n\n* 30 minutes speaking in English\n* 30 minutes speaki
 ng in Spanish\n* 30 minutes speaking in English\n* 30 minutes speaking in 
 Spanish\n\n**Beginner Room (Optional and only Mondays)**\nWelcome\, Englis
 h and Spanish beginners.\n\nPlease note that **we speak half of the time i
 n English and half in Spanish.** We help each other learn both languages.\
 n\n**After two hours**\, everyone returns to the main room to meet all par
 ticipants and take a group screenshot. If you have time\, you’re welcome
  to stay and continue the conversation for as long as you like.\n\n**Commu
 nity**\n**We have 9 MeetUp groups meeting at the same time** (Mexico City\
 , Calgary\, Vancouver\, Toronto\, New York\, London\, Los Angeles\, Medell
 in\, and Santiago de Chile). However\, during the exchange\, you will meet
  people not only from these cities but also from all over the world.\n\nYo
 u can get the link to our 9 MeetUp groups by visiting any of the following
  pages:\n[https://se-habla.com/spanish-meetup/](https://se-habla.com/spani
 sh-meetup/)\n[https://se-habla.com/english-meetup/](https://se-habla.com/e
 nglish-meetup/)\n\n**One-Time Donation**\nFor over four years\, the meetin
 gs were free\, but starting last October\, I am requesting a **ONE-TIME DO
 NATION** to access the meetings and help to cover the costs of the 9 MeetU
 p Groups.\n\nYou can make the one-time donation at the link below. Afterwa
 rd\, PayPal will redirect you to a page where you'll find the Zoom link to
  join the meeting.\n[https://se-habla.com/language-exchange/](https://se-h
 abla.com/language-exchange/)\n\nIf you have already made a donation and do
 n't have the Zoom link\, please contact me.\n\n**Please don’t hesitate t
 o reach out if you have any further questions.**\n\nSee you soon\,\n**Héc
 tor Fuentes**
